  "id": "adv_main_01_05_04",
  "title": "星見編1章25話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "よろしくぅ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nice to meet ya!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "よ、よろしくお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-same here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.199999976158142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、まだグループの名前決まってないんでしょ？\n芽衣、いいの考えてきたんだー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ you still haven’t decided on a group name‚ right?\nI came up with a great one!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.70000002384186,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "命名！　メイドーナッツ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Listen to this… Mei Donuts!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.099999833106995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "その……どうしてドーナツ……なのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… Why donuts?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.449999737739564,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣が好きだからだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "‘Cause Mei likes ‘em.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.48653023242951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "あなたの好みで名前を決められても……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We can’t just decide based on your preference…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.46460275650025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "名前は後でみんなで話し合って決めるとして\nまずは部屋を決めないとな。ええと空いてる部屋は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can all talk about it and decide on a name later.\nWe’ll need to decide on her room first. Which ones are available…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.63126947085063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣、{user}さんと\n一緒の部屋にしよっかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know what‚ {user}-san?\nMei can just share a room with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.80665931079701,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "おい、誤解されるようなこと言わないでくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "C’mon‚ don’t say things that can be taken the wrong way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.438911008834864,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\nちょっと、話があります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…\nI need to talk with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.62242352621896,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "え、ええと……後じゃ、ダメかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "U-um… Can we talk after this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.12217621803284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_corridor-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae02",
      "startTime": 55.02217621803284
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 55.38884288469955
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "本当に、あの子を\n私達のグループに入れるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that girl\nreally going to join our group?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.88884288469955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……ああ、そのつもりだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… That’s the plan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.28884288469955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ聞きますが、グループにとって\n彼女の存在がプラスになるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let me ask you this. Do you really think\nshe has anything to contribute to our group?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.6055095036825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あると俺は思っている……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I do think she does.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.36251638730371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "なんです？　さくら達の方に入る怜さんは\nダンスの大会で優勝しているんですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What would that be? Rei‚ the girl joining Sakura’s group‚\nshe’s won a dance championship‚ hasn’t she?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.24584972063704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ああ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-right…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.84584972063703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "彼女は何かあるんですか？\n歌がうまいとか、ダンスが凄いとか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What has Mei accomplished?\nIs she an amazing singer or dancer?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.22566827138269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "か……可愛い……とか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s… cute?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.32566827312118,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ち、違うよ。琴乃達より可愛いとかいう話じゃなく\n可愛さのタイプが違うというか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "D-don’t get me wrong. I’m not saying she’s cuter than the rest of you.\nShe just has a different kind of cuteness.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.03730101759236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "……よーく、分かりました\n彼女のこと気に入っていることが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ I understand you just fine.\nShe’s your favorite.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.93730101759228,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "待て待て、違う。グループに必要だと思ったんだ\n空気を変える必要があると思うんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait‚ no‚ it’s not like that. I feel like she has what your group needs.\nI think the overall mood of the group needs to change.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.2004774587849,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "…………空気？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…The mood?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.7004774587849,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃達は向上心も高くて真面目だ。でもそれは\nアイドルに大切な遊び心がないとも言える",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono‚ you and your team are ambitious and dedicated.\nAs an idol‚ that can be interpreted as lacking a sense of fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.90047745878483,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "けどああいう子と一緒に活動することで\n琴乃達にも新たな発見があると思うんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But by working with a girl like that‚\nI think you can all discover a new side to yourselves.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.4224957324562,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.4542077876625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "ああ……お気に入りとか\nそういうことで決める訳ない。信じて欲しい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I do. I’d never make a decision\nbased on favoritism. You can trust me on that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.60763182813896,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "…………分かりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Very well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.6272462703285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\nいつまで話しているの？　早く早く",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!\nHow long are you gonna be talking for? Come on!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.42724627032857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_04-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "何恥ずかしがってるの？\n一緒に塀の上でデートした仲なのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you acting all shy now?\nDon’t tell me you forgot our date on the wall.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.57368614052712,
